Thank you for contacting us. You can replace cards online under Fleet Manager > Cards > View Cards. Click Select > Reissue to the right of a card, and on the following screen select a Reason for Reissue in the dropdown menu. Lost or Stolen will cancel the existing card, whereas Damaged will keep it active. Please let me know if you have any questions. 

